                "invention-title": [
                    "Uranium ore in-situ leaching-hydrogen storage-CO2 storage system and method based on electrolyzed water driving",
                    "基于电解水驱动的铀矿地浸-储氢-CO2封存系统与方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a uranium ore in-situ leaching-hydrogen storage-CO2 storage system and method based on water electrolysis driving, and belongs to the technical field of metal ore leaching mining. The system comprises an electrolyzed water system, a sandstone uranium ore leaching system, an H2 collection system and an intelligent regulation and control system, oxygen generated by the electrolyzed water system is conveyed into a high-temperature heating device of the sandstone uranium ore leaching system through an O2 conveying pipe, and hydrogen generated by the electrolyzed water system is conveyed into an H2 storage tank of the H2 collection system through an H2 conveying pipe; the intelligent monitoring system is connected with the electrolyzed water system and the sandstone uranium ore leaching system through signal transmission lines, and intelligent regulation and control of the whole system are achieved. According to the system, H2 and O2 are generated by electrolyzing water, the generated H2 is used for hydrogen energy storage, the O2 is used for neutral leaching of the sandstone uranium ore, CO2 is injected in the leaching process to realize storage of the CO2, and a triaxial press and a high-temperature heating device are combined to simulate the high-temperature and high-pressure environment of in-situ leaching of the sandstone uranium ore. The system is helpful for realizing a more sustainable and clean energy system."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种基于电解水驱动的铀矿地浸‑储氢‑CO2封存系统与方法，属于金属矿溶浸开采技术领域。该系统包括电解水体系、砂岩铀矿浸出体系、H2收集体系和智能调控体系，电解水体系产生的氧气通过O2输送管输送至砂岩铀矿浸出体系的高温加热装置中，电解水体系产生的氢气通过H2输送管输送至H2收集体系的H2储罐中，智能监测体系通过信号传输线与电解水体系、砂岩铀矿浸出体系连接，实现全系统的智能调控。该系统通过电解水生成H2和O2，产生的H2进行氢气储能，O2用于砂岩铀矿的中性浸出，并在浸出过程中通过注入CO2，实现CO2的封存，将三轴压力机与高温加热装置结合模拟砂岩铀矿原位浸出的高温高压环境。该系统有助于实现更可持续、清洁的能源体系。"
                }
